20 the Arkansas State Fair and Livestock Show Association for state assistance
21 to cities and counties, is amended to read as follows:
22 (5) The Arkansas State Fair and Livestock Show Association or
23 its bond trustee shall receive the moneys listed in this subdivision (a)(5),
24 less any general revenues appropriated to the Arkansas State Fair and
25 Livestock Show:
